### Problem Description

Lucene 10.1.0 on ES 9.0.x exhibits EOF for certain queries.

In particular, it must be a boolean query with a multi-claused `must_not` disjunction.



### Steps to Reproduce

N/A (yet)

Here is an example query:

```
        {
          "bool": {
            "filter": [
              {
                "bool": {
                  "filter": [
                    "< multiple term clauses>"
                  ],
                  "must_not": [
                    {
                      "terms": {
                        "<field>": [
                          "<many_values>"
                        ]
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "terms": {
                        "<field>": [
                          "<many_values>"
                        ]
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "term": {
                        "<field>": {
                          "value": "<value>"
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "terms": {
                        "<field>": [
                          "<many_values>"
                        ]
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ],
            "must": {
              "query": {
                "multi_match": {
                  "fields": [
                    "<many_fields>"
                  ],
                  "minimum_should_match": "custom should match",
                  "query": "<QUERY>",
                  "type": "most_fields"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
```

